  "mixStrategy": "Ultra-sparse, low-register layering for deep sleep. Bass provides a warm sub-foundation (C1-C3) with long sustained root notes. Warm Pad chords sit in the C3-C5 range with slow, ghostly voicings that blend into the bass harmonics. Vibraphone melody floats in C4-C5 with predominantly descending motion, placed spectrally above the pad but never piercing. All tracks share the same near-static harmonic rhythm (chord changes every ~16-22 seconds): Cm \u2192 Abmaj \u2192 Bbmaj (i \u2192 bVI \u2192 bVII). No rhythmic pulse \u2014 notes drift in freely with staggered entrances. Maximum 3-4 notes sounding simultaneously. Energy arc: 0.4 at start, gently fading to 0.2 by end. Everything whisper-quiet, like a warm blanket of sound dissolving into darkness.",
